high_descs: Turn around and head towards the sidetable.
Pick the wateringcan from the table.
Move around and walk towards the shelf.
Keep the wateringcan on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Pick the WateringCan from the table and keep the WateringCan on the Shelf.

high_descs: Go to the sidetable straight ahead.
Pick up the wateringcan that is on the table.
Turn around and go to the shelf behind you.
Put the wateringcan on the shelf next to the black cauldron.
anns.task_desc: Move a WateringCan from the table to the Shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and turn left to the side table.
Pick the watering can from the side table.
Place the watering can on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: To place the watering can on the shelf.
